<user-mapping>
  <!-- Sinister Mesh OS — Guacamole user mapping
       Author: RKOJ-ELENO :: 2026-05-24
       Default operator login. CHANGE THE PASSWORD on first real deployment;
       this stub exists so the container starts. -->
